channel.title: Searching for a Project [I have VPS]
channel.description:
Hey. Im searching for a Partner. I've got a Vps 24/7 (8gb ram, high internetspeed, no laggs). I need a Partner who got or who know how to make a custom webclient (a selfmade webclient). If u got a server running but u dont got a hoster i could host it for you but you need to have a webclient.
MSN: L-tt@hotmail.de
btw; soz for my bad English. Im German
